      &lt;img alt="" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/h3POuGkEb2F3GUF46BYQpLVyJK4=/188x0:2213x1350/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73641888/Ring_Smart_Video_Search2.0.jpg" /&gt;
